\par }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid7473308\charrsid13855502 Choir }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid13855502 2: }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 Glory to the Father, and to the Son, * and to the Holy Spirit.
